<h1 id="suspend-leave" sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Suspend leave</h1>

<p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">You can suspend leave for an employee to stop leave accruals from being processed for selected leave types.</p>
<h2 id="suspend-leave-and-absence-for-an-employee" sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Suspend leave and absence for an employee</h2>
<ol sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">On the employee's record, select <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Leave</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Select <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">Suspend leave</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">Select <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">New</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">In the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Suspend leave accrual</strong> dialog box, select the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Leave type</strong> along with the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Start date</strong> and <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">End date</strong> for the suspension.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Optionally, you can add a <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Comment</strong> for the suspension.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-suspend-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">If accruals are processed while the employee's leave is suspended, no accrual will be made for the suspended leave types.</p>
